race.comment: KING KRYPTOS (6) was a touch disappointing at the latest effort but the two wins prior were good enough for a race of this nature. Can bounce right back to form without surprising. RICH MINX (2) goes well for hoop Sandkuhl who has two wins and two placings from just four rides. Again gets the benefit of her 3kg claim and shapes as a leading contender. OBEROI PRINCESS (7) has placed two of three first-up and may run a race while fresh. PARTY SPIRIT (3) is another who races well first run back from a break with two wins and three placings from just six attempts. Has to be included in calculations. ROTHGO (4) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be discounted lightly.
